HEADWORD: Accumb
<hw>Ac*cumb"</hw> <pr>(⟦acr⟧k*k⟦ucr⟧mb")</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>accumbere</ets>; <ets>ad</ets> + <ets>cumbere</ets> (only in
